{"tid":1524380,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"而家應該立即籌備全港無限期大罷工","createTime":"2019-08-31T17:06:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T05:12:36.000Z","uid":135158,"like":58,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"5a5be615efd74c4e0ce9ed0a7469515d736d537c","tid":1524380,"uid":135158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:06:46.000Z","msg":"所有嘅革命第一步必先係罷工開始<br />\n從經濟壓力遂步脅迫比單係街頭上對抗有效一百倍<br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭成個國家由示威初期就已經開始宣佈罷工<br />\n但係六月開始到呢家香港幾乎冇任何關於呢樣野嘅討論，就算係8月5嗰次都只係半桶水嘅罷工<br />\n你老尾，一路對抗政府一路幫政府賺錢成件事根本就係on9到仆街<br />\n<br />\n仲有唔好同我講有人手停口停冇工返好撚慘<br />\n呢班人喺社會上係極少數，正常香港人點都會有積蓄留低<br />\n同埋一旦送中過左外國一制裁香港，佢地一樣會冇飯開，遲啲早啲有咩分別?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人係咪仲覺得搵錢緊要過爭取民主自由?<br />\n如果係嘅話，呢場運動不如盡早宣告收皮仲好，因為香港人唔撚配有民主"},{"pid":"e5bd69d6a7f619ac8a7a5655904fc1a7efc88baf","tid":1524380,"uid":34334,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:07:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"31b3bbaf77756faf671f1ecc2c013ce2b10256c0","tid":1524380,"uid":168522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:09:20.000Z","msg":"真係要時間<br />\n今次2/9 3/9 宣傳準備完全唔夠<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7dbe3476af9bb1030a4fd61f53b332de1b3609f","tid":1524380,"uid":295662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:11:56.000Z","msg":"罷一日都唔肯 點無限期罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8df0d44e9b99ea8910aa146d3724ef4942506d83","tid":1524380,"uid":298142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:12:24.000Z","msg":"我次次都請假罷 , 返去又比上面仆街管理層清算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fb9